  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Creates a single, streamlined process whereby a facility or program operating both a pre-kindergarten program and a daycare program may apply for and receive any certification, licensing, or other requirement otherwise necessary to operate a pre-kindergarten program or daycare program under the laws of the state."
